I"ï	<ul>
  <li>From <a href="https://elk.zone/devdilettante.com/@roland/111067680184544895">Mastodon</a>: Today I Learned, RMagick doesnâ€™t support <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">smush</code> (<a href="https://imagemagick.org/script/command-line-options.php#smush">imagemagick docs for smush</a>) to align horizontal images at the bottom but <a href="https://github.com/minimagick/minimagick">MiniMagick</a> does! Stack Overflow:<a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/60357036/imagemagick-montage-how-to-align-images-to-bottom">imagemagick montage - how to align images to bottom</a></li>
</ul>

